It took only a few moments to the communication station to establish a
secure channel with Maximal Base. Tyrael crossed his arms and started.

Tyrael: Greetings, Rodimus. I have talked with my superiors and we
have determined that a cease-fire should be the best thing for both
our groups right now. Thus, I, Major Tyrael of the Tripredacus Army,
offer you, Maximal Commander Rodimus Prime, a pact of non-agression
between our two factions. What do you say?
